## 9. Roles & Responsibilities
| Role | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| [CTO / Head of Engineering] | Owns this plan; declares disasters; directs technical recovery. |
| [Engineering On-Call / SRE] | Executes recovery runbooks; validates restores. |
| [Security Officer] | Confirms security controls are intact post-recovery; coordinates with IR. |
| [Privacy Officer] | Confirms PHI safeguards during and after recovery. |
| [Database / Platform Owner] | Maintains backup/replication configuration and restore procedures. |
| All Engineering | Keep runbooks and IaC current; participate in DR tests. |

See `../governance/roles-and-responsibilities.md.template` for full role definitions.

## 10. Exceptions
Exceptions to this plan require documented risk acceptance per `../governance/exceptions-and-waivers.md.template`, approved by the [CTO] and [Security Officer], time-bound, and recorded in the exceptions log.

## 11. Compliance, Monitoring & Enforcement
Compliance is verified through DR test completion, RTO/RPO achievement, backup-restore validation, and corrective-action closure, reported to management review (`../governance/management-review.md.template`). Violations are handled per `../people/hr-security-policy.md.template`.

